  #introduction.column.size1of2
    h3.hidden About
    :markdown
      This is a [jQuery](http://www.jquery.com "jQuery") plugin for displaying galeries
      and other content the way *you* want.

      Checkout the different presets in the upper menu!
      Especially the [Gallery](examples/gallery.html "Rondell Gallery preset") and [Thumbnails](examples/thumbnails.html "Rondell Thumbnails preset") preset.

      The rondell demos can be controlled with your keyboard,
      by clicking the controls or by clicking the rondell items.

      Touching items and swiping on a phone or tablet computer will work too!

      The plugin has been tested with and should work fine with:
      IE 7-9, Firefox 3.6+, Chrome, Safari 4+, Opera 11+

      Licensed under the [MIT license](http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php "MIT licence").

    p
